Commentary Text: Chahal to Agarwal, out Bowled!! Chahal might prove to be expensive, but he'll make sure to get at least a wicket or two. Tosses this legbreak and entices the batsman to have a go at it. Agarwal obliges, swings across the line and misses altogether. The leg-stump goes for a toss and KXIP lose their first wicket.
